Do you think stuff like quadratic
functions will be useful in my future?

150
00:08:26,110 --> 00:08:27,020
How should I know?

151
00:08:27,020 --> 00:08:30,440
Anyway, why am I helping you with your homework?!

152
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:32,280
Hey, your eyes are too close.

153
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:36,030
