169
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,740
Uh... Classmate.

170
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:23,540
What? Aren't you a bit old for that?

171
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:26,000
Don't fall for me.

172
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,130
