173
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:33,510
Well, you <i>do</i> seem to have pluck. I like that about you.

174
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:35,840
That's right. Yukito-san is a really nice guy.

175
00:09:37,010 --> 00:09:39,010
All right. He can stay.

176
00:09:39,090 --> 00:09:40,010
You're serious?

177
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:42,140
