179
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:46,270
First, you sleep in the shed.

180
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:47,100
And second...

181
00:09:48,350 --> 00:09:50,110
You will be my drinking partner.

182
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:56,450
