207
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:16,230
Hey, there's nothing wrong with having no talent!

208
00:11:16,230 --> 00:11:18,030
Let's drink up and forget about it, huh?

209
00:11:20,070 --> 00:11:23,490
My name's Haruko. Kamio Haruko.

210
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:25,450
One more drink, ma'am.

211
