219
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,690
You're a funny guy, aren't you?

220
00:11:51,690 --> 00:11:52,350
Am I?

221
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:55,770
I may not look like it, but I have a pretty good eye for men.

222
00:11:55,770 --> 00:11:57,440
