359
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:53,460
We young girls are in trouble!

360
00:19:55,290 --> 00:19:57,000
Wow, did you hear that sound?

361
00:19:58,300 --> 00:20:00,420
Kamio-san, who is this?

362
00:20:00,420 --> 00:20:05,140
