363
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:06,760
A traveler?

364
00:20:06,760 --> 00:20:10,430
A homeless, perverted kidnapper? He's a lost cause, right?

365
00:20:23,990 --> 00:20:27,490
Kamio-san, I think we'd better be going.

366
00:20:27,490 --> 00:20:30,950
What? But I was doing really well blowing bubbles.

367
00:20:30,950 --> 00:20:33,620
Let's do it some more. Kami-Kami can join us, too.

368
00:20:33,620 --> 00:20:35,330
Kami-Kami? Is that me?

369
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:39,590
It's getting dark, so let's do it again tomorrow.

370
00:20:39,590 --> 00:20:41,840
I'll pack a lunch for us.

371
00:20:44,630 --> 00:20:47,300
